<i>adverb</i>: 얼쩡얼쩡 [얼쩡얼쩡], 얼씬얼씬 [얼씬얼씬], 얼씬 [얼씬], 알짱알짱 [알짱알짱], 알랑알랑 [알랑알랑] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>얼쩡얼쩡 [얼쩡얼쩡]</dt><br>
<dd>1. loiteringly</dd><br>
<dd>하는 일 없이 자꾸 이리저리 돌아다니거나 빙빙 도는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of wandering around or turning round and round with no purpose.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flatteringly</dd><br>
<dd>남의 마음에 들려고 아첨을 하며 능청스럽게 계속 남을 속이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of constantly deceiving another person in a sly manner while flattering him/her to win favor.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>얼씬얼씬 [얼씬얼씬]</dt><br>
<dd>1. briefly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 장소나 눈앞에 잠깐씩 나타났다 없어졌다 하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of appearing for a moment and disappearing in front of a place or one's eyes again and again.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flatteringly</dd><br>
<dd>교묘한 말과 행동으로 계속해서 남의 비위를 맞추는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of trying to please another person with sly words and behavior again and again.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>얼씬 [얼씬]</dt><br>
<dd>1. briefly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 장소나 눈앞에 잠깐 나타났다 없어지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of appearing for a moment and disappearing in front of a place or one's eyes.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flatteringly</dd><br>
<dd>교묘한 말과 행동으로 남의 비위를 맞추는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of trying to please another person with sly words and behavior.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>알짱알짱 [알짱알짱]</dt><br>
<dd>1. flatteringly; with flattery</dd><br>
<dd>남의 마음에 들려고 아첨을 하며 계속 남을 속이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of deceiving someone continuously while flattering him/her to gain favor.</dd><br>
<dd>2. loiteringly</dd><br>
<dd>하는 일도 없이 자꾸 돌아다니거나 앞에서 왔다 갔다 하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of moving around or pacing around idly in front of someone.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>알랑알랑 [알랑알랑]</dt><br>
<dd>flatteringly; with flattery; fawningly</dd><br>
<dd>남의 비위를 맞추거나 남에게 잘 보이려고 자꾸 아첨을 떠는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of fawning on someone in order to please or gain favor with him/her.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>